{"tid":1943791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"起初，6月9日年青人被扑頭的時候，我沉默了","createTime":"2020-03-26T03:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T04:20:19.000Z","uid":21255,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd3fe4d547463543c4665a3f0dc3098a1c39bd2","tid":1943791,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"起初，6月9日年青人被扑頭的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是年青人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們7月21日轉身離開的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為分手說不出來。<br />\n<br />\n當他們8月31日在鐵路打人的時後，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我一向自駕。<br />\n<br />\n當他們11月11日射殺手無寸鐵的人時，<br />\n我沉默了，因為晚上才做生意。<br />\n<br />\n最後當他們禁我賣酒時，<br />\n我再沒生意做了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8507beb8a49ec26a390877f84f9b8784a31b1d1f","tid":1943791,"uid":21255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"人地叫封關時你班酒吧狗去曬邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c124f97c7525ab75337ac212e5e3d3d80607b5","tid":1943791,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"Ho ball!"},{"pid":"82c898e7a9e2df308d7cf3672f26094b7c0024b1","tid":1943791,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"d2000344aa101e829730bd00bc3da88e0ada13f2","tid":1943791,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"秦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb26b4002a6e92369ef19691a990c8526a15b72","tid":1943791,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,